  <div class="page">

    <div class="sec">SECTION 3 — DÉPARTS / DEPARTURES</div>

    <p class="qtitle">S3Q01 : Combien de départs avez-vous enregistrés du 1er Janvier {{surveyYear}} à ce jour ? / How
      many departures did you register from the 1st of January {{surveyYear}} to the present day?</p>
